Title: Carnivores
Plot: Mackey and the Strike Team mediate a dispute between Rondell Robinson and the Nation of Islam while Wagenbach and Wyms investigate a brutal home invasion in the tight lipped Korean community.  Meanwhile, Aceveda revisits his past.
GuestStars: David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Walter Jones, Brent Roam, June Kyoto Lu, Sandra Purpuro, Mailon Rivera, Camillia Sanes, Sticky Fingaz, Cedric Pendleton, Efrain Figueroa, Katy Boyer
